This is a <%= property.sqft %> square foot, 
<%= property.occupancy_type %> <%= property.property_type %> 
located in <%= property.city %>, <%= property.state %>.

It has <%= property.bedrooms.to_i %> bedroom<%= (property.bedrooms.to_i != 1) ? "s" : "" %>,
<%= property.bathrooms.to_i %> full bathroom<%= (property.bathrooms.to_i != 1) ? "s" : "" %>,
<% if ((property.bathrooms.to_f - property.bathrooms.to_i)*10 > 0) %>
	<%= ((property.bathrooms.to_f - property.bathrooms.to_i)*10).to_i %> half bathroom<%= (((property.bathrooms.to_f - property.bathrooms.to_i)*10).to_i != 1) ? "s" : "" %>,
<% end %>

<% if property.property_type == 'house' %>
	and is situated on <%= property.lot %> acres of land.
<% elsif property.property_type == 'condo' || 'apartment' || '' %>
	and is on the <%= property.floor.to_i == 0 ? "ground": property.floor.to_i.ordinalize %> floor.
<% end %>